        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Public Health Air Quality Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to take specified actions related to monitoring and improving air quality, including by implementing a program to administer or conduct emissions measurement and quantification, promulgating regulations related to specified source categories, and deploying not fewer than 1,000 air quality sensors.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
